videos.description: Jacob Eason connects with Cade Otton on a three-yard pass to score the Huskies' first touchdown of the game vs. Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Otton finds Eason for easy Washington TD) 2019/10/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eason finds Otton for easy Washington TD

videos.description: Davis Mills connects with a wide-open Simi Fehoko in stride to score a 42-yard Stanford touchdown to take a 13-7 lead over Washington.
